CyeLoFi copyright 2012 Andrea Di Dato
http://adicon.lahost.org/

CyeLoFi is an open source project to remotely control your telescope with any
smart device like phones and PDAs.


    The code in this project is free software: you can redistribute it and/or
    modify it under the terms of the GNU General Public License as published
