    GNU General Public License for more details.

    You should have received a copy of the GNU General Public License
    along with this program. If not, see <http://www.gnu.org/licenses/>.


CyeLoFi is a combination of hardware and software. This code represent the
software layer needed to hack an OpenWRT supported hardware and made it able
to connect to your telescope mount and give access to it throught WiFi.

For a steep by steep guide to build your own CyeLoFi, please visit:
   http://adicon.lahost.org/CyeLoFi
   https://github.com/adicon/CyeLoFi/wiki


